doctype html
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="utf-8")
        meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no")
        meta(
            name="description"
            content="Integrum Systems is an engineering-first company building maintainable, open professional systems. Learn about our mission, approach, and the people behind the work."
        )
        meta(name="author" content="Integrum Systems")

        title About — Integrum Systems

        // Favicon
        link(rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="assets/favicon.ico")

        include includes/css.pug

    body.d-flex.flex-column.h-100
        main.flex-shrink-0
            // Navigation
            include includes/navbar.pug

            // Page header
            header.bg-fog.py-5.border-bottom
                .container.py-4(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    .row.justify-content-center
                        .col-lg-8.text-center
                            h1.display-6.fw-bolder.mb-3 Built on engineering discipline.
                            p.lead.mb-0
                                | Integrum is structured around a long-horizon commitment to systems that can be understood, maintained, and trusted.

            // Founding context
            section.py-5
                .container.py-4(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    .row.justify-content-center
                        .col-lg-7
                            h2.fw-bolder.mb-3 Why Integrum exists.
                            p.mb-3
                                | The gap between hobbyist tools and enterprise platforms is wide, expensive, and often filled with vendor lock-in. Research teams, independent engineers, and early technical organizations operate in this gap daily — building on systems that are underdocumented, unserviceable, or priced out of their range.
                            p.mb-0
                                | Integrum was founded to close that gap. We build infrastructure-grade systems that are open by default, staged for long service life, and designed for the people doing the actual technical work.

            // Founder block
            section.py-5.bg-fog
                .container.py-4(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                        .col-lg-4.text-center.mb-4.mb-lg-0
                            img.img-fluid.rounded(
                                src="https://dummyimage.com/400x400/D7DEE8/243041"
                                alt="[PLACEHOLDER: Founder name] — Founder, Integrum Systems"
                                style="max-width: 280px"
                            )
                        .col-lg-8
                            h2.fw-bolder.mb-1 [PLACEHOLDER: Cameron Last Name]
                            p.font-mono.small.mb-3(style="color: #3b4a5e") Founder, Integrum Systems
                            p.mb-0
                                | [PLACEHOLDER: 3–5 sentences. Technical background and domain, what you have built or worked on previously, and why this problem space. Be specific — degrees, prior roles, and relevant projects are appropriate. Avoid "passionate about" constructions.]

            // Operating principles
            section.py-5
                .container.py-4(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    .row.justify-content-center
                        .col-lg-7
                            h2.fw-bolder.mb-3 How we operate.
                            p.mb-3
                                | These are not aspirational values. They are structural commitments that shape how we build and communicate.
                            ul.mb-0
                                li.mb-2 We publish our constraints. If a system has limits, we document them.
                                li.mb-2 We admit tradeoffs. Transparency builds authority.
                                li.mb-2 We version visibly. Changelogs, migrations, and lifecycle notices are not optional.
                                li.mb-2 We avoid artificial urgency. No countdown timers. No fake scarcity.
                                li We document like engineers, not marketers.

            // CTA strip
            section.py-5.bg-primary
                .container.text-center.py-3(style="max-width: 1200px")
                    h2.fw-bolder.text-white.mb-2 Work with us.
                    p.text-white.mb-4(style="opacity: 0.9")
                        | We engage at the architecture and system level. If you have a well-defined problem or an early-stage technical challenge, we want to hear about it.
                    a.btn.btn-light.btn-lg.px-4(href="contact.html") Get in touch

        // Footer
        include includes/footer.pug

        include includes/scripts.pug
